These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile, scooter, trike
1. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
2. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
3. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the snowmobile##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |     3      |  4   |
| Transport   | trike | skateboard | snowmobile | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, photography, singing
1. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
2. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |       4       |
| Hobby   | card-games | singing | gardening | photography |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, mechanic, entrepreneur, nurse
1. the mechanic is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
2. the mechanic is on the far left or far right##3
3. the accountant is the accountant##1
4. the accountant is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job   | nurse | accountant | entrepreneur | mechanic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-4::.
