2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | board-games | woodworking | fishing | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, satire, animation, time-travel
1. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching animation movies##2
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching animation movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | satire | time-travel | thriller |

