.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, puzzles, traveling, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | collecting | puzzles | traveling | fishing |

