.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-15::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, chinchilla, bird, rat
1. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the rat and the owner of the dog##2
3. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |    2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | rat | chinchilla | dog | bird |

